node.text:
Happy Birthday Flexy 😭😍🥰
No words or pictures will ever do justice for how much I love this 8 year old puppy soul boy! Big boy! Flex has traveled all over the country with us and changed my life forever. America’s dog! Flex, if you’re reading this from your iBone since apparently all dogs have an IG, I love you more than you’ll ever know!! Stay kyoot ❤️✌🏼
